headline: Jacobs to Support Rail Expansion for Major LA-Area Port Facility
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been awarded a contract to provide construction management for the Port of Long Beach's Pier B On-Dock Rail Support Facility program. This project is a cornerstone of the port's $2.2 billion program to enhance cargo movement efficiency, reduce environmental impacts and support regional economic development.
